item.title: How would Nebraska Football stack against the Big 12 if they never left?
item.description: With the recent events that Nebraska Football has had to endure with the Big Ten Conference in the recent year many fans have come out to say Nebraska should move on. Many fans have wanted Nebraska to maybe go back to that old friend down the street, the Big 12 Conference. Nebraska has been out of the Big 12 for almost a decade and it would be cool to reunite with their old rivals.

item.title: How did the Blue Bloods fare from the 2020 season to 2021?
item.description: The 2021 College Basketball season has been hard for many especially with the COVID-19 pandemic.We have seen many teams struggle even for the Blue Bloods of league.
